ref=\"/de/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Die Methode&nbsp;<code><strong>Node.removeChild()</strong></code>&nbsp;entfernt einen Kindknoten aus dem DOM. Gibt den entfernten Knoten zurück.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>var oldChild</em> = <em>element</em>.removeChild(<em>child</em>);\n<strong>ODER</strong>\n<em>element</em>.removeChild(<em>child</em>);\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>child</code> ist der Kindknoten, der aus dem DOM entfernt werden soll.</li>\n <li><code>element</code> is der Elternknoten von&nbsp;<code>child</code>.</li>\n <li><code>oldChild</code> hält eine Referenz auf&nbsp;den entfernten Kindknoten. <code>oldChild</code> === <code>child</code>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Der entfernte Kindknoten bleibt im Speicher erhalten, ist aber nicht länger Teil des DOM. Mit der ersten Syntax-Form ist es möglich, den entfernten Knoten später im Code wieder zu verwenden, über die&nbsp;<code>oldChild</code>&nbsp;Objektreferenz. In der zweiten Form wird jedoch keine&nbsp;<code style=\"font-style: normal;\">oldChild</code>-Refernenz&nbsp;behalten, also wird (vorausgesetzt dass nirgendwo anders im Code eine Referenz gehalten wird) der Knoten unbenutzbar und nicht erreichbar, und wird nach kurzer Zeit&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Memory_Management\">automatisch aus dem Speicher entfernt</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Wenn&nbsp;<code>child</code>&nbsp;kein Kind des Knotens&nbsp;<code>element</code> ist, wirft die Methode eine Exception. Dies passiert auch wenn&nbsp;<code>child</code>&nbsp;zwar zum Aufruf der Methode ein Kind von&nbsp;<code>element</code>&nbsp;war, aber durch einen beim Entfernen des Knotens aufgerufenen Event Handler bereits aus dem DOM entfernt wurde (z.B. blur).</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;!-- Beispiel HTML --&gt;\n\n&lt;div id=\"top\" align=\"center\"&gt;\n  &lt;div id=\"nested\"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Ein bestimmtes Element entfernen, wenn der Elternknoten bekannt ist</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> d <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"top\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> d_nested <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"nested\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> throwawayNode <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> d<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>d_nested<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Ein bestimmtes Element entfernen, ohne den Elternknoten zu kennen</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"nested\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parentNode<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Alle Kindknoten eines Elements entfernen</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"top\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>element<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>firstChild<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/REC-DOM-Level-1/level-one-core.html#method-removeChild\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 1 Core: removeChild</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Core/core.html#ID-1734834066\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 2 Core: removeChild</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-3-Core/core.html#ID-1734834066\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM Level 3 Core: removeChild</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>Node.replaceChild</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/parentNode\"><code>Node.parentNode</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/remove\"><code>ChildNode.remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"example"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"specification"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"Die Methode Node.removeChild() entfernt einen Kindknoten aus dem DOM. Gibt den entfernten Knoten zurück.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.removeChild()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.removeChild()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.removeChild","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.removeChild()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"element.removeChild","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Node.removeChild","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Node.removeChild","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.removeChild","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Node.removeChild()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/node/removechild","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/node/removechild/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node","title":"Node"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild","title":"Node.removeChild()"}],"pageTitle":"Node.removeChild() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}